function Test-IPv4 {
<#
    .SYNOPSIS
        Tests if parameter matches IPv4 pattern.
    .DESCRIPTION
        Author    : Dmitry Gancho, dmitry.gancho@ctl.io
        Last edit : 11/18/2015
        Version   : 1.0
    .PARAMETER Ip
        IP to test
    .EXAMPLE
